relation: Darrow2 - #22 Although Jeff has a strong desire for picnic lunches, the memories are too painful for him to eat another one. Fortunately, that favorite cake isn't going to waste.
Darrow2 - #23 Working their way to Fourside, our heroes come to the realization that sanctuaries actually exist all around them. Just not officially, I guess.
Darrow2 - #24 A familiar group comes into the picture, with an all too familiar problem. Perhaps Ness should become their new agent. Heck, even King would be a step in a better direction.

Darrow2 - #25 Without much choice in the matter, Ness and friends leave the Runaway Five to their fate. Sure, they may be trapped for eternity, but hey, that just means more chances to see them live. Cheer up, Ness!
Darrow2 - #26 Live in comic form! It's the Runaway Five! Aaaaaiiiieee!!
